author: Divya Rao
title: Holiday Photos: Kareena Kapoor Khan Looks Like A Million Bucks In London
text:
Divya Rao Mar . 27 . 2017 
Kareena Kapoor Khan has had a busy year with her pregnancy. Post giving birth to baby Taimur , one would’ve thought she’d take some time off and rest, but the actress is busy gearing up for Veerey Di Wedding. Such a workaholic, Bebo! She’s currently in London with Saif Ali Khan and Taimur – possibly for Sunita Kapoor ‘s 60th birthday. Here are some pictures of them doing the rounds…. and man, does she look incredible! Spotted: Kareena with her designer friend Faraz Manan pic.twitter.com/WgEVGzCwpY
